class_notes: This section is for NNP students only. Online with some synchronous sessions.
course_description: This course focuses on developmental and molecular genetics and our ability to recognize genetic disorders and to determine genetic variations that predispose individuals to disease.
prerequisites: NRSG 528 or equivalent transfer credit as co-requisite.
